sources.title: Jailbreak | Full Movie | Action Adventure Prison Breakout
sources.description:
A criminal mastermind, a former LAPD explosives expert, has seized control of a maximum-security prison and recruited the inmates as his army. Now, this criminal powerhouse faces off against a rogue hostage negotiator and a retired Black Ops agent, who had been visiting his incarcerated son at the facility.
2023.  Stars: Louis Mandylor, Kristos Andrews, Brian Krause, Tom Sizemore
